      "comment": "IS HE HAPPY (4) comes off an average run last start when fifth at this track over 410m behind Hara Hachi Bu (23.58) in a Grade 4/5. Has ability and looks hard to stop. GUITAR TANGO (8) produced a modest effort most recently when eighth at this track over 410m behind Bundy Paradise (24.05) in a Grade 5. The form out of his last race has been franked. Shapes as one to consider. LEKTRA ROSA (2) was resuming when finishing sixth at Mt Gambier in a Grade 5 (18.21). Will strip fitter for the run. One of the main contenders. ELLIOT NOVA (5) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
